---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Section, Button } from '@/components/ui';
---

<Layout
  title="Our Story - Sharing Heritage Through Children's Books | Roots On Rise"
  description="Discover how a mother's journey inspired Roots On Rise - creating children's books that connect kids to culture, mythology, and heritage through beautiful storytelling."
  showAnnouncement={false}
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <Section background="tertiary" container="md">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h1 class="font-title font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-dark mb-6">
        <span class="text-primary">our</span> story
      </h1>
      <p class="text-dark/70 text-lg">
        A mother's journey to share the beauty of Hindu culture with the world.
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <!-- Story Content -->
  <Section container="md">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2 class="font-title font-bold text-3xl text-dark mb-8">
        üôè Namaste!
      </h2>

      <p class="text-dark/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Welcome to our world of cultural exploration! We're so glad you're here.
      </p>

      <p class="text-dark/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Roots On Rise began with a simple desire: to share the rich cultural heritage of <em>India (Bharat)</em> with our children. As parents raising kids far from our homeland, we found ourselves telling stories about our mythology, our many Gods and Goddesses, and the timeless wisdom of our ancestors.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-tertiary p-8 rounded-lg my-8">
        <p class="text-dark/80 text-lg leading-relaxed italic">
          "We realized that most products - books, games, and related materials - did not spark curiosity in children to learn more about India, and did not evoke pride in our rich civilization."
        </p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-dark/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        This inspired us to create our first children's illustration book, <strong class="text-primary">"The Marvelous Hindu Deities"</strong>, which quickly became a favorite with our kids and many others like them.
      </p>

      <p class="text-dark/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Encouraged by the book's popularity and driven by a deep passion for sharing our rich South Asian heritage and culture with the world, we created <strong>Roots On Rise</strong> ‚Äî a platform to unveil cultural treasures through playful learning and personal discovery.
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-title font-bold text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-6">
        Our Mission
      </h3>

      <p class="text-dark/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Our products are designed to bring engaging and immersive experiences into our homes, and cultivate a deep connection to our collective roots, mythology and history.
      </p>

      <p class="text-dark/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Join us on this exciting adventure as we craft products that not only entertain but also serve as windows into the vibrant tapestry of rich traditions. Together, let's nurture a global community of young learners who celebrate their rich cultural identities!
      </p>

      <h3 class="font-title font-bold text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-6">
        Our Vision
      </h3>

      <p class="text-dark/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
        While we began with Hindu and Indian heritage, our vision extends far beyond. We dream of bringing people and cultures together from across the world ‚Äî helping the next generation discover the richness, wisdom, and beauty found in every tradition. By celebrating what makes each culture unique, we hope to foster appreciation, understanding, and a true sense of <strong class="text-primary">unity in diversity</strong>.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-dark text-light p-8 rounded-lg my-8">
        <img
          src="/images/brand/Brand-Logo-Name-Transparent-Background.svg"
          alt="Roots On Rise"
          class="h-12 w-auto brightness-0 invert mb-4"
        />
        <p class="text-xl font-title font-bold mb-2">Thanks for joining us.</p>
        <p class="text-light/70">‚Äî The Roots On Rise Team</p>
        <p class="text-light/50 text-sm mt-2">Questions? Reach us at support@rootsonrise.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-12">
      <Button asChild>
        <a href="/books">Explore Our Books</a>
      </Button>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>
